name: 'HISTORY WHAT MAKES US TODAY' TSHIRTS
description:
The 'Sher Soorma' project has been put together by Gupsy Aujla & The Anglo Sikh Heritage Trail (ASHT). Aiming to try and raise awareness and promote the forgotten legacy of the Sikh Regiment.
 
To coincide with the release a special T-Shirt has been made avaliable to purchase 'HISTORY IS WHAT MAKES US TODAY'.

Supporting the cause includes the likes of the world famous Sukshinder singh shinda, monty panesar, tigerstyle and many more!

10% will go to the anglo sikh heritage trail

name: BHANGRA SAMPLES VOLUME 1
description:
SAVE £5..PRICE DROP FROM £15.99


Bhangra Samples Vol 1

 

High quality samples of traditional Bhangra/punjabi instruments. This CD provides 100's of samples that can be used to help make them hits. Recorded by top musicians and in high quality recording you can find endless loops and samples.

The samples are copyright free and those who buy the cd will have rights for releasing.

 

This CD provides samples of the following:-

 

DHOL

DHOLKI

TABLA

SARANGI

FLUTE

MANDOLIN

TADD

ALGOZEY

TUMBI

BANJO

BACKING VOCALS




THIS CD IS A MUST FOR ALL PRODUCERS AND BEATMAKERS AND WILL HAVE YOU SPOILT FOR CHOICE WHEN SELECTING LOOPS FOR YOUR MASTERPICES.

 

EACH INSTRUMENT PIECE IS LABELLED WITH THE KEY IT IS PLAYED IN AND THE TEMPO IT WAS RECORDED AT SO IT IS EASY TO FIND WHAT YOU ARE AFTER.



THE SAMPLES ARE IN WAV FORMAT (24 BIT /44.1 KHz) FOR USE WITH CUBASE REASON LOGIC FRUITY LOOPS SONAR ACID PRO TOOLS ETC.. BASICALLY ANY SOFTWARE THAT SUPPORTS WAV FORMAT FILES.
